 />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:50:52.000Z","msg":"除左資訊外 好重要係佢通常都會做下代購/生意<br />\n唔用wechat都唔知點contact個客同中國親戚(通常個邊都有個人接頭)又唔交稅<br />\n佢地冇左wechat真係唔知點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e689a1be2fe6159aef9695ae1180bbe0aa6fed","tid":2157221,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:07:35.000Z","msg":"有樣野叫對等，<br />\n你放whatsapp 我咪放wechat囉，簡單。"},{"pid":"8df317b406dd2ea95ad8a135ec54c2d59cd9dafc","tid":2157221,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d52593d1065cc8e587caab91ebf977bc842207b0","tid":2157221,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:34:26.000Z","msg":"pin this<br />\n<br />\n原po: <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/latimes/status/1293581763055366147?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flatimes%2Fstatus%2F1293581763055366147%3Fs%3D19&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8QoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=e915f26b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flatimes%2Fstatus%2F1293581763055366147%3Fs%3D19&h=8b5a1a20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/latimes/status/1293581763055366147?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n大家入去屌鳩班支畜啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:08:22.000Z","msg":"清醒鬼佬comment: <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><em><br />\nI don&rsquo;t agree what the Chinese interviewee said in this article, &ldquo;We always use WeChat because everyone else uses it. It&rsquo;s like Facebook messenger but ten times better, ten times more sophisticated.&rdquo; How so? Wechat, like many other Chinese apps, is a tool to monitor people.<br />\n<br />\nCant stand trump but tbh this was a good move. The CCP has consistently been stealing our data and intellectual property for as long as we can remember. Its shitty for the families but the world needs to step up and not allow the ccp the do this shit anymore<br />\n<br />\nWhat about allowing WhatsApp in China?</em><br />\n<br />\nON9: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<em>More asian American voters against Trump I assume. Keep it up Donnie ... doing great work!!! Grinning face with smiling eyesThumbs up<br />\nTo America Chinese ... I feel for you but hang in there, someone will find another way for you to stay in touch with family. <br />\nVote better. Let's build a better America and world.</em>"},{"pid":"02aff67d8ac2330c20179ebdbc37e2657fbf45b9","tid":2157221,"uid":271130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:10:01.000Z","msg":"中國人不等如共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢班南加州中國人一定係比共產黨好嚴咁監控緊先會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f90be9b63d541b62761e3d0c1b2d2885be72a91","tid":2157221,"uid":2752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"296359dfdcc50be0f1de2dbef2be8611c05bcb6a","tid":2157221,"uid":121146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:13:59.000Z","msg":"真心覺得好笑  支共唔開放  美國點解要開放比你？ 北韓洗唔洗又整個app比d脫北者聯絡用？ 咁得閒叫美國開放比佢用d軍企app  點解唔叫支共開放個網絡世界比自己國民？ 倒行逆思  on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:13:26.000Z","msg":"取易不取難<br />\n美國你點屌都無事<br />\n支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc935eed47637ee8bba7bab5cbc18a09215738c","tid":2157221,"uid":17443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cea63ad5c9a756d9acecae591a4fb75074fb6c56","tid":2157221,"uid":124439,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T02:02:43.000Z","msg":"叫中國開通WHATSAPP咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:20:41.000Z","msg":"開放無用，whatsapp上面都係假消息，wechat先比到佢地圍爐取暖"},{"pid":"16ca83569c0c0b2dca2ea4640909e6a042e35944","tid":2157221,"uid":76261,"like":0,